quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,45,"Uye zvirokwazvo kumaThamood takatumira mukoma wavo Swaalih achiti: “Namatai Allah (voga).” Uye tarisai! Vakava mapoka maviri achikakavadzana pakati pavo"
  27,46,"Akati: “Imi vanhu vangu! Sei muchimhanyira kutsvaga zvakaipa zvakanaka musati mazvitsvaga? Sei musingatsvagi ruregerero rwaAllah, kuti muve munowana tsitsi?”"
  27,47,"Vakati: “Tinoona kuti une munyama neavo vanewe.” Akati: “Zvakaipa zvenyu zvina Allah, asi muri vanhu varikuedzwa.”"
  27,48,"Uye muguta maiva nevarume vapfumbamwe (kubva kuvana vemadzimambo avo) vaiita zvakashata munzvimbo, uye havana kumbozvishandura"
  27,49,"Vakati: “Pikai naAllah umwe kune umwe kuti tichauraya muchivande usiku iye (Swaalih) uye nemhuri yake, uye mushure mezvo tichati kune hama dzake: ‘Hatina kumboona kufa kwake iye nemhuri yake, uye zvirokwazvo, tirikutaura chokwadi.’”"
  27,50,"Saka vakaronga urongwa, uye isu takaronga urongwa, ivo vasingazivi"
  27,51,"Uye ona kuti magumo eavo vakaronga aiva akaita sei! Zvirokwazvo, takavaparadza ivo nevanhu vavo pamwechete"
  27,52,"Idzi ndidzo dzimba dzavo dzakaparadzwa zvachose nekuda kwekutadza kwavo. Zvirokwazvo, umu mune chidzidzo kuvanhu vanoziva"
  27,53,"Uye takadzivirira avo vanotenda uye vaitya Allah, uye vachiita mabasa vachifadza ivo"
  27,54,"Uye (rangarirai) Loti paakati kuvanhu vake: “Munoita here zvivi (chingochani) muchiona (zviri pachena)?”"
  27,55,"“Munoita here chidaka chenyu (chevakadzi) kuvarume muchisiya vakadzi? Zvirokwazvo, muri vanhu vasingazivi vanotadza.”"